Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏联遭受了55年来最严重的小麦减产
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波兰发生工人和农民暴动\N苏联军队入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古巴和尼加拉瓜的军队数量达到500,000\N萨尔瓦多和洪都拉斯政府垮台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绿党控制了西德议会\N要求从欧洲的土地上撤走核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥陷入动荡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北大西洋公约组织解体\N美国独木难支
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,片名：赤色黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺身而出而非胆小怯懦\N后者永远理解不了胜负的真谛——罗斯福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢让我搭车  -没啥\N- Thanks for the ride.- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么安排吗？\NWhat's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续上路，否则没时间吃早饭了\NGet going,we don't have time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还要工作什么的吧？\NAre you working or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我要整天待在加油站  你搭便车回家吧\NYeah, I'll be at the station all day.You'll have to hitch a ride home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -你今天训练了吗？\N- All right.- You got practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们练了双倍的时间\NAfter that, we're on double time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我可练了三倍  -你可真没志气\N- Triple.- You should be ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去就带个输样\NYou think they'd take it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，伙计，你也输过\NCome on, bud.You lost a football game once yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么？-我不记得了\N- What?- I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可记得\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在撒谎  -回头见\N- I think you're lying.- Catch you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真不知道该不该相信你  -彼此彼此\N- I never know when to believe your mouth.- Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-回见，伙计  -回见，杰德\N- Later, bud.- See ya, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你的历史作业做了没？-做了一点\N- So, did you do your history?- Yeah, some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇家狩猎队伍\NMR. TEASDALE: And the great hunt would always begin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是以半圆形阵容散开\Nwith the armies spread out in a semi-circle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到能包围罗德岛那么大面积\NI would say about the size of Rhode Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们会冲锋陷阵，驱赶前面的一切\NThen they would ride forward,driving everything before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野兽、人甚至小虫都不能幸免\NBeasts, men, even bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后，他们的队形会收缩成一个圆形包围圈\NNow, the ends would kind of close in to form a shrinking circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:04:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圈内所有猎物都急着逃跑\NEverything within that circle panicked to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时，狩猎的蒙古战士们\NWhen the Mongols could see each other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会开始大开杀戒\Nthey had worked themselves up into a pretty good frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狩猎开始后\NNow, when this killing started,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可能持续数日、数周\Nit'd last for days, weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至数月\Neven months.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀戮会一直持续\NAnd it went on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到可汗的幼子\Nuntil the young son of the Khan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恳求父亲放生\Nasked his father that the last creature alive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一只猎物\Nbe allowed to go free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐，同学们\NWell, now, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-天呐  -到处都是伞兵\N- Well, now.- GIRL: They're all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-来看看  -好啊\NBOY 1: Check it out.BOY 2: All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们好酷啊\NBOY 1: They look pretty cool though, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也许是偏离航道了吧\NMR. TEASDALE: I would say they were way off-course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可真少见\NThis is very unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄语\N(CHATTERING IN RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办，戴先生\NThen do something, Mr. Teasdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄语\N(MEN CHATTERING IN RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄语\N(SPEAKING RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，朋友\NWhat's going on, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄语\N(OFFICER ORDERING IN RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达里尔，快走\NDaryl, come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去\NGet in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下！趴下！\NGet down, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-进来！-等等\N- Get in!- Wait. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家卧倒！\NEverybody down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑！快进来！\NRun! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\NStay down.\N-9
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非我死了\N他们才能从我冰冷的手里拿到我的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远处的枪声\N(DISTANT MACHINE GUN FIRE)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿图罗\NArturo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西班牙语\N(CALLING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\NPapa! Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下！我爸还在那里\N- Get down!- My father's back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\NROBERT: Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-爸爸，他们进城了，-怎么回事？\N- Dad, they're in town.- What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们向我开枪！他们在向所有人开枪！\NThey were shooting at me!They're shooting at everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喷气发动机的轰鸣\N(JET ENGINE ROARING)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得上山去，离开这儿\NWe're going to the mountains.Getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看出来他们是什么人吗？\NMR. MORRIS: Who are they,near as you can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听到他们有人说西班牙语\NBOY: I heard some of them speaking Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你看到他们了吗？-说西班牙语？\N- Did you see any of them?- DANNY: With Spain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是谁？\NMR. MORRIS: Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拜托，冷静  -天呐！\N- BOY: Come on, man, just relax.- Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-冷静点  -小伙子们！\NBOY: Just take it easy.MR. MORRIS: Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上进去拿睡袋和吃的，快点\NGet in there and get sleeping bags and food. Right now. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-别磨蹭！-快去\N- Let's move it!- Come on, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿干粮，别拿糖果、曲奇之类的食物\NTake the dry stuff. Don't mess around with candy or cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\NGot it. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我该拿什么？-纸巾\N- What should I get?- Plenty of Kleenex.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拿上枪  -去拿灯\N- .308.- JED: Somebody get some lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点38子弹\N.38 Specials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.17,0:08:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿点手纸，我可不想用树叶\NGrab some toilet paper.I ain't using leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多拿些点22子弹\NMR. MORRIS: The.22's. Carry a lot of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有电池，能拿多少拿多少\NTake a lot of batteries, boys.All the batteries you can carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有猎枪\NThere's a shotgun there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带上那些上衣\NJED: Get those down jackets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈特，小心\NMatt, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\NGet down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直升机接近\N(HELICOPTER APPROACHING)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\NLay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的飞机吗？\NIs it ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你，儿子  -我也爱你，爸爸\N- I love you, boy.- I love you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-告诉妈妈我爱她  -好的\N- Tell Mom I love her.- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好照顾她的\NI'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，来吧，孩子们，快离开这里\NAll right, come on, boys,just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走，别回来了\NCome on. Don't come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管看到和听到什么，都别回来\NNo matter what you see or hear,don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就会来接你们的\NI'll come and get you soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开杂物箱\NOpen the glove compartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是这样吗？-是的\N- Is it there?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上子弹\NLoad it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,压满了\NIt's already loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我\NGive it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还要这个吗？-要，放在我口袋里\N- Want these also, Jed?- Yeah, put them in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-上帝啊！-天呐！\NJED: Oh, Jesus Christ!MATT: Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，上帝\NOh, Jesus! Oh, Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上急转弯\NI'm gonna turn off quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直升机！\NROBERT: It's a helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美军直升机\NIt's ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上车\NGet in! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-查出问题了吗？-是的\N- Get it?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查出来了\NThat's got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在唯一的问题是：水没了\NOnly thing is we got one problem.We don't have any water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撒尿怎样？\NHow about pissing in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好主意，开始尿吧  -你怎么知道能行？\N- That's a good idea. Get up here.- How do you know it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你多大了？小子\NHow old are you, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15啦  我是丹尼，不是“小子”\NFifteen. And the name's Danny, not kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大了就会知道了\NWell, when you grow up,you'll know these things, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我上去，往散热器上撒尿\NNow get up here and piss in the radiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（士兵说西班牙语）\N(SOLDIERS SPEAKING SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（西班牙语）美国坦克正从平原上驶来\N(IN SPANISH) We've got Yankee tanks coming in from the plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去了大部分夜视镜\NWe've lost most of our night vision
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反坦克导弹也不多了\Nand have only a few anti-tank missiles left for shooting at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让精锐部队带火箭筒到猎杀组去\NPut your best men into hunter groups armed with RPG's.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每组保持100米距离\NKeep 100 meters between each group,dig holes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等美国佬过来偷袭\Nwait until the Yankees approach to strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就给他们来个瓮中捉鳖\Nfind out from where they attack, then combine your groups and attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命，贝拉长官\NYes, Mr. Bella.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里需要防空火力\NI want some anti-aircraft here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在部署，长官\NWe're working on it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…简直是疯人院\NThis... This is a madhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）你要见我吗？\N(IN RUSSIAN) Do you want to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）是的，到体育用品店去\N(IN RUSSIAN) Yes, yes.Go to the sporting goods store.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到4473号档案\NFrom the files obtain forms 4473.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里会有武器清单\NThese will contain descriptions of weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及货主名单\Nand lists of private ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们家人呢？他们怎么办？\NDANNY: But our families, huh? What about them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要待在山上躲一阵\NROBERT: We gotta stay up here and hide awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想回家\NI just wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想躲起来  家人会找不到我的\NI don't wanna hide.If I hide, they'll never find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来看看\NCheck it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这帮我们躲了一颗子弹\NStopped a bullet that would have hit somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有这个\NI got these.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们很有用\NThose'll do us a lot of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有无线电\NWe've got no radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说，我们光靠橄榄油和饭糊\NI mean, how long do you think we can survive up here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在这荒山上坚持多久？\Non olives and Rice Krispies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然我们还能怎样？\NWhat else are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为学生会主席\NAs Calumet Student Body President,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提议我们投降\NI forward the motion that we give ourselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意  我们不能老待在这里  我们需要…\NI second the motion. We can't stay here. We need stuff and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下，丹尼\NSit down, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们哪都不能去，现在城里太危险了\NYou're not going anywhere.It's too dangerous to go into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们投票决定吧  -不行\N- I say we vote on it.- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四分卫同志，现在不是在比赛，他想到哪都行\NThis isn't the big game, Mr. Quarterback.He can go wherever he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N(FIRMLY) No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个傻帽\NYou're such a goddamn jock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，冷静点\NHey. Come on, guys. Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牢骚声\N(GRUNTS)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那么想回去，就带上你的破行李滚吧\NYou want to go so bad.Here, haul ass. Take your shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也一样\NThat goes for the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在给你们机会，走吧\NThis is your chance. Get walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面正在打第三次世界大战\NIt is World War III down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百姓死伤惨重\NPeople are being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些可能是苏联人\NThose could be Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰德\NJed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人咋办？\NWhat about your family, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少我还活着\NBut I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要留下来\NAnd I'm staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人也会希望我能幸存\NMy family would want me to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人也会这么想的\NYour family would want you to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为自己很聪明，其实你们只是胆小鬼\NYou think you're so smart, man.But you're just a bunch of scared kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你算老几？\NWhat do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤家寡人\NAlone, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你不孤单\NNo, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来，伙计\NHere, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？\NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听你的\NI'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NJED: All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人走吧\NThe rest of you get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下也行，不过\NAll right, but if you stay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想留下就得听我的，明白？\Nyou're gonna do exactly what I say, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么样？-明白\N- Huh?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来烤火吧\NSo come on over here and get warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达瑞尔\NDaryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很抱歉\NMe too, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在…\NNow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和迈特从小就和父亲一起上山露营\NMatt and I've been coming up to these mountains with our dad all of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会打猎、捕鱼，可以在这山上待很长时间\NWe can hunt, we can fish,we can stay up here a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要待多长时间？\NHow long, Jed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喷气发动机的轰鸣\N(JET ENGINES ROARING)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到听不到敌机声音为止\NTill we don't hear that no more.\N-10
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十月\NOCTOBER\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打中它了\NI got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NYou got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要好好吃… -它还活着\N- Gonna eat good...- He's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开第二枪\NNever shoot twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然，印第安人会闻声赶来\NShoot twice, they can find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它反正已经死了\NHe's dead, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道？\NHow do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前常读杰德和吉米的冒险故事\NI used to read a lot about Jedediah Smith and Jim Bridger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你开两枪，印第安人就会赶来\NThe Blackfeet, if you shot twice,would know right where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我爸给我取名为杰德\NMy dad named me after Jed Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你第一次捕获猎物，对吧？\NThis is your first time, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪又怎样？\NYeah. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝猎物的血庆祝\NYou gotta drink if it's your first. We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么味道？\NWhat's it taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太糟\NIt's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像牛排那样咸，也有流鼻血的感觉\NIt's kinda salty like a steak or when you've got a nosebleed, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要喝，这是鹿的精华\NYou gotta do it. It's the spirit of the deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是真正的猎人就得喝\NWhen you drink it, you'll be a real hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干杯\NBottoms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\NGo. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一饮而尽，伙计\NGo. Go for it, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NAll right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不赖嘛\NYou did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和它的血融为一体了  我爸常说…\NHis blood is yours. You know,my dad said that once you do that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从此就不再一样了\Nthere's gonna be something different about you. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道还行\NIt wasn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太难喝\NIt wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不错\NWasn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了橄榄，只有这个了\NThat's the last of it, except for the olives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有很多肉\NWe've still got plenty of meat left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你射杀的鹿\NJust stuff you shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说…\NSo tell me, dork,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然汉堡是哪来的？\Nwhere do you suppose hamburgers come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人会射杀它们\NNobody shoots them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要吃的\NWe need food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要情报\NWe need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此\NWe do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们进城去\NWe'll go into town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝\NJED: Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也没人\NThere's no one in here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这坦克好像已报废上千年\NIt's like it's been here for 1,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸟叫声\N(BIRD CAWING)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商店还开着\NHey! The stores are open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是人，也许战争已经结束了\NThere's people everywhere.Maybe it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！\NHey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-别轻举妄动  -那不是美军\N- Don't go anywhere.- Those aren't our troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里怎么看得清\NYou can't tell from here, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-上帝啊  -哪是什么？\NMATT: Jesus Christ.JED: What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我从没见过这样的坦克  -我也没见过\N- I've never seen a tank like that before.- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都隐蔽起来了，肯定有鬼\NROBERT: Yeah, but they're packed.That means something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先把东西藏好\NJED: Let's stash our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就放在这吧  -好主意\N- Leave it all here, okay?- Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是市长的车\NThat's the mayor's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们抢走了达瑞尔父亲的车\NThey got Daryl's dad's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-看看那坦克多大  -天呐\N- Look at the size of that tank.- Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（耳语）路易斯，路易斯你好吗？\NMATT: (WHISPERING) Louis.Louis, how you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为啥害怕我们？\NWas he scared of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.03,0:22:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们问艾丽西亚吧，她肯定知道\NLet's ask Alicia. She'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要六个牙刷\NSix toothbrushes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-杰德  -嗨，你姐姐好吗？\N- Oh, Jed.- Hi. How's your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么？你们从哪儿来？-我们躲在山上…\N- What? Where'd you come from?- The mountains, we've been hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们疯了？快离开这里\NAre you crazy? You gotta get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会的，但要先知道这到底是怎么回事\NWe will, but first we gotta find out what's going...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白\NYou don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道你们每个人  他们正在通缉你们\NThey know who all of you are.They're looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁要抓我们？-克格勃\N- Who?- The KGB.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.71,0:23:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-苏联人？-还有古巴人\N- The Russians?- And the Cubans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古巴人\NThe Cubans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.81,0:23:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过俺爹吗？\NLook, have you seen my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话也没人接\NI called, there was no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了加油站，也空无一人\NI went by the station, it was empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\NOkay, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得告诉你一些秘密\NI'm gonna tell you something I'm not supposed to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不能说，可是\NNobody is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是什么？\NBut what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们带走了很多人\NThey took a lot of people away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些他们觉得会制造麻烦的人\NPeople that they thought were gonna make trouble for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些有枪或者他们想要东西的人\NPeople that had guns or things they wanted. They just took them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带到哪儿？\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们称之为劳改营的地方\NRe-education camps.That's what they call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说他们吧很多人带到……杰德\NThe drive-in. I heard they took a lot of people to... Jed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你祈祷\NI pray for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国是个淫窝\NMAN ON PA: America is a whorehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先辈的理想\Nwhere the revolutionary ideals of your forefathers
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已被资本主义毒草玷污\Nare corrupted and sold in alleys by vendors of capitalism
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们自由战士的誓言，只能使你们变得脑满肠肥\NYou grow fat on the pledge of freedom fighters
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（宣传继续）\N(PROPAGANDA CONTINUES)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.25,0:24:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-嗨  -干嘛？\N- Hey.- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.35,0:24:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆，你能找到我爸吗？我是杰德\NCould you find my dad, Tom Eckert?I'm Jed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.72,0:24:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-杰德？迈特？-巴尼斯先生？\N- Jed? Matt?- Mr. Barnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.83,0:24:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子，我会找到你爹的  我知道他在哪\NLaddie, I'll go find your dad.I know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.73,0:24:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道莫理斯市场吗？\NYou know Morris' Market?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.53,0:24:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公路上那个  你顺便看看莫理斯先生还在哪儿不？\NThe one on the highway.Can you see if Mr. Morris is in there, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.84,0:24:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会四处找他的\NI'll look around for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.87,0:25:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（女人抽泣）\N(WOMAN SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.19,0:25:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\NDaddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.33,0:25:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，我能站起来\NIt's all right. I can stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.20,0:25:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们\NBoys.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.80,0:25:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\NDaddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.34,0:25:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰德\NJed...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.70,0:25:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\NMATT: Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.61,0:25:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说话，让我看看你\NDon't talk. Don't say anything.Let me look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.11,0:25:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道\NYeah, I knew I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.02,0:25:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道了\NI knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.82,0:25:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着\NYou're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.76,0:25:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直严格训练你们\NI was tough on both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.86,0:25:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们那么严格\NI did things that made you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们那时很讨厌我\Nmade you hate me sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.97,0:25:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在明白我的苦心了吧？\NYou understand now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.84,0:26:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了，爸爸？怎么来到这里？他们把你怎么了？\NWhat happened, Dad?Why are you here? What'd they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.51,0:26:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\NDoesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.18,0:26:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正不管怎样\NOne way or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.35,0:26:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生自古谁无死\None reason or another, we're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.72,0:26:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会结束\NIt's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.39,0:26:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得…\NRemember...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.79,0:26:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得以前在公园玩的时光吗？\NRemember when you used to go in the park and play?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.36,0:26:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你们放在秋千上\NAnd I used to put you on the swings,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.13,0:26:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时你们俩…\Nand both of you were
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.27,0:26:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是小不点\Nso damn little that...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.68,0:26:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得，我全都记得\NI remember. I remember all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.65,0:26:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你们摔倒我就不能从旁照顾了\NWell, I ain't gonna be around to pick you up when you fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.28,0:26:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在要自己照顾自己\NBoth of you got to take care of each other now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.52,0:26:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们再也见不到你了，爸爸\NWe'll never see you again, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.19,0:26:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的  我不想听这话，迈特\NYes, you will.I don't want to hear that, Mattie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.63,0:27:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈怎么样了？她在哪？\NWhat happened to Mom? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.84,0:27:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在可没时间哭了\NWe can't afford to be crying anymore now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.01,0:27:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你们俩再为我哭了\NI don't want either of you to ever cry for me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.52,0:27:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再哭了\NDon't ever do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.58,0:27:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要还活着就该庆幸\NNot as long as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.22,0:27:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸在哪？埃克特先生\NWhere's my dad, Mr. Eckert?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.86,0:27:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，孩子\NI don't know, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.96,0:27:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.33,0:27:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他们找到你们之前\NYou all get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.04,0:27:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们赶快走吧\NGet out before they find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.71,0:27:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\NDad,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.85,0:27:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，我也爱你们\NI know you do, Son. I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们\NBoys!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.74,0:28:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我报仇\NAvenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我报仇\NAvenge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.61,0:28:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，汤姆\NCome on, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.20,0:28:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真该死\NI'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.90,0:28:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-快进来  -梅森先生，你怎么样？\N- Get in here before somebody sees you.\N- Mr. Mason, how're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.34,0:28:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-幸会  -你好，梅森先生\N- Good to see you.- Hello, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.37,0:28:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（梅森太太咯咯地笑）\N(MRS. MASON GIGGLING)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.81,0:28:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我给你们盛些汤  -我这不是窝藏罪犯嘛\N- I'll get you boys some soup.- We got us some outlaws here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.05,0:28:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于有房子住了\NWow, a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.48,0:29:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐\NBoys, find a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.28,0:29:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前五周都是露宿山林\NI haven't been in a house for five weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.29,0:29:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你走运\NYou look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.23,0:29:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起的这几个是谁？\NWho you got out there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼，达瑞尔\NWe got Danny, we got Daryl...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.67,0:29:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们几个已经到FA了呢\NWell, we all figured you boys were headed for F.A. By now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么是FA？\NWhat's F.A.?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.34,0:29:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由美国  那是安全地带\NFree America. That's the safe zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.74,0:29:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在哪里？\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.44,0:29:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在敌占区\NHell, you boys is in occupied territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.95,0:29:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们离前线40英里\NYou're 40 miles behind enemy lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.55,0:29:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正深陷第三次世界大战\NRight smack-dab in the middle of World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.86,0:29:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个在城里晃悠想干嘛？\NWhat are you boys doing fooling around town anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.86,0:29:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在搜集情报，梅森先生\NWe've been looking for news, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.03,0:29:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争一开始我们就与世隔绝\NWe haven't seen or talked to anybody since it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.73,0:29:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这等等\NWait here just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.74,0:29:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能有更多食物\NI wish there was more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.21,0:30:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.41,0:30:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，梅森太太，我们非常感激\NThank you, Mrs. Mason.We really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.55,0:30:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，喝点暖暖身子吧\NHere, this'll keep you boys warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.12,0:30:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这个来判断自己方位\NUse this to see where you're standing from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.26,0:30:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无线电？梅森先生，我们不能拿你的无线电\NA radio? Mr. Mason, we can't take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.16,0:30:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，我还有一个\NThat's all right. I got another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.77,0:30:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，你们听着\NNow, you boys listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.94,0:30:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再到卡路美特了\NDon't go to Calumet no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.27,0:30:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\NHow come?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.71,0:30:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那里老有袭击事件\NBecause there's been some attacks up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.31,0:30:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那里的人都被割破喉咙\NPeople waking up with their throats cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.31,0:30:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-听说你也被杀了  -没有\N- Word has it, it's you.- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.36,0:30:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸妈怎么了？\NWhat happened to my dad and mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.33,0:30:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗伯特，你爸死了\NYour daddy's dead, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.93,0:30:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们枪杀了他\NThey shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.97,0:31:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏联人发现有些枪丢失了\NThe Russians found some guns missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.00,0:31:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就以协助游击队的罪名枪杀了他\Nso they shot him for aiding guerillas.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“协助游击队”？他从没帮过任何人\NWhat do you mean '"aiding guerillas'"?He never aided anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.18,0:31:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是我们偷的  -我们害死了他\N- We took the stuff.- We killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.38,0:31:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们杀他，是想杀一儆百\NThey killed him, son.Made him an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.22,0:31:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们好好听着，给我记住\NNow, you boys listen to me and let that burn in real good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.63,0:31:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你妈在哪，罗伯特\NI don't know where your mother is, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.09,0:31:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有亲人了\NI ain't got nobody now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.30,0:31:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们需要吃的、睡的什么的，尽管来找我\NYou boys need food, a bed,you need anything, you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.67,0:31:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有些传家宝想托付给你们\NI got a couple of heirlooms I want to hide with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.31,0:31:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰克，别！\NJack, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.85,0:31:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的孙女\NMy granddaughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.15,0:31:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们藏在这两天了\NThey spent two days sneaking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.89,0:31:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些混蛋一直想找到她们\NThose sons of bitches tried having their way with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.47,0:32:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托妮，艾丽卡，这是迈特和杰德\NToni, Erica, this is Matt and Jed Eckert.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.24,0:32:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会照顾你们的\NThey're gonna take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.97,0:32:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想知道他们要到哪去\NI don't wanna know where they're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.28,0:32:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，爷爷\NBye, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.12,0:32:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-梅森先生  -谢谢你\N- Mr. Mason.- Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.06,0:32:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅森先生\NWell, Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.76,0:32:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们好运\NGood luck, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.76,0:32:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有一盒子弹\NHere's a box of ammo for your granddaddy's pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.44,0:32:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -祝你们好运\N- Thanks.- Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.64,0:32:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好照顾她们，放心\NI'll take care of them. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.35,0:33:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是自由美国电台，现在是11:59\NWOMAN: It's 11:59 at Radio Free America
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.89,0:33:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山姆大叔的音乐节目以及《黎明前的真相》\NThis is Uncle Sam with music and the truth until dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.69,0:33:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我有话要传给…\NRight now, I've got a few words
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.23,0:33:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌占区的同胞们\Nfor our some of our brothers and sisters in the occupied zone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.63,0:33:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椅子已经靠在墙上  椅子已经靠在墙上\NThe chair is against the wall.The chair is against the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.90,0:33:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰有把长胡子  约翰有把长胡子\NJohn has a long mustache.John has a long mustache
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.97,0:33:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是12点，美国同胞们，离胜利又近了一天\NIt's 12:00, Americans,another day closer to victory
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.97,0:33:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是自由区还是敌占区的同胞\NAnd for all you out there on or behind the lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.68,0:33:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌都献给你们\Nthis is your song
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.91,0:33:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（战斗圣歌）\N(BATTLE  HYMN OF THE REPUBLIC PLAYING)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.80,0:33:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在形势不同了\NThings are different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.93,0:34:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们来了  -没错\N- They're coming up.- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.73,0:34:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们告诉其他人吧\NLet's go tell the others.\N-11
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.73,0:34:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉巴霍国家森林
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.21,0:34:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）真美\N(IN RUSSIAN) Oh, how beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.33,0:34:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这写着什么？\NWhat is written here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.47,0:34:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是学过英文吗，翻一下\NYou studied English. Translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对美国历史可是非常了解\NAmerican history. I know this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.31,0:35:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（清喉咙）\N(CLEARS THROAT)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.18,0:35:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉巴霍人(北美印第安人部落)国家战场遗址\N'"Arapaho National Battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.25,0:35:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1908年，这里发生了一场惊天动地的印第安农民起义\N'"Here was a great peasant uprising in 1908 of wild Indians.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.59,0:35:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被罗斯福总统率领牛仔和资本主义军队\N'"They were crushed by President Theodore Roosevelt
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.62,0:35:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功镇压\N'"leading imperialist armies and cowboys.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.76,0:35:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇压持续了一个冬天\N'"The battle lasted all winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.30,0:35:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35,000人被屠戮\N'"More than 35,000 were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是美国西部最惊人的镇压之一\N'"It was the greatest battle of the American West.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.37,0:35:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好极了！\NBravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.27,0:35:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤里，站在这儿，我给你拍一张\NYuri, stay here. I'll take a photo of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.22,0:35:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像非洲狒狒\NAfrican baboon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.75,0:35:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该你了\NNow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.32,0:35:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来，朋友\NCome here, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.03,0:35:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，笨蛋\NHurry up, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.98,0:36:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我，尤里\NLook at me, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.62,0:36:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.95,0:36:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看我找到什么了\NLook what I've found.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.39,0:36:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一支箭\NAn arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.65,0:36:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一支印第安箭\NAn Indian arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.46,0:36:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个哲学家\NWhat a philosopher you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.02,0:36:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,印第安人还用钢\NI did not know the Indians used steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.96,0:36:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了，笨蛋  他们用缴获的美军武器改造的\NSure, you fool, they used the melted sabers of Federalist Cossacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.73,0:36:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,印第安人还用塑料？\NDid these Indians work in plastic, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.57,0:36:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋，这是打磨过的骨头  这肯定有更多\NYou idiot, this is bone, polished to a high sheen. There must be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.41,0:36:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.78,0:36:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,树丛那边\NNear the brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.48,0:36:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（英语）姑娘，你在干嘛\N(IN ENGLISH) Girl! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.52,0:36:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）别去！保持距离，她有武器\N(IN RUSSIAN) Stop! Keep your distance.She has a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.29,0:36:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）不许动，该死的\N(IN RUSSIAN) Stop, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.99,0:36:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（机枪射击）\N(MACHINE GUN FIRING)
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.56,0:37:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快，抓住她\NQuickly. Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.47,0:37:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找掩护\NTake cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.24,0:37:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）站住\N(IN RUSSIAN) Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.48,0:37:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（大声说）\N(EXCLAIMS)
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.95,0:37:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）帮帮我，同志\N(IN RUSSIAN) Help me, comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.85,0:37:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她\NGrab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.79,0:37:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抓住她了\NI got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.83,0:37:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）我要死了\N(IN RUSSIAN) I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.62,0:38:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）上帝，救救我\N(IN RUSSIAN) God help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.72,0:38:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救我\NGod help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.08,0:38:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪声\N(GUN FIRES)
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.55,0:39:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回声\N(ECHOING)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.45,0:39:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸟的啼叫\N(BIRDS CAWING)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.47,0:39:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也是人\NBut they were people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.57,0:39:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸也是人\NYeah, well, so was my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.07,0:39:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么气味\NWhat was it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.51,0:39:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很好\NIt was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.05,0:39:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事是肯定的\NOne thing is for sure now,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.25,0:39:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谁也不能再回家了\Nno one can ever go home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.46,0:39:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不行了\NNever.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.63,0:39:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也做点贡献吧\NWhy don't you make yourself useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.93,0:39:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来洗\NYou wash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.13,0:39:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们再也不负责洗刷了\N我们和你们男生一样出色\NWe're never doing your washing again!\NMe and her is as good as any of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.60,0:39:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们他妈搞什么鬼？\NSo what's up your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.94,0:39:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.74,0:40:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再这样说了\NDon't you ever say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.68,0:40:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听见没？再说我就杀了你\NHear me? Say that again, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.88,0:40:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到没？我会杀了你\NHear me? I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.12,0:40:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说错什么了？\NSo what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.66,0:40:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说粗话了\NWhat you said was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.67,0:41:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（西班牙语）从今以后\N(IN SPANISH) From now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.21,0:41:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班以下人数的队伍…\Nall troops are forbidden to travel outside secured areas
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.51,0:41:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得涉足非安全地带\Nin any group smaller than squad size.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.32,0:41:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续西班牙语\N(ACKNOWLEDGES IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.95,0:41:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知布拉琴科\NThen call Bratchenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.12,0:41:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八区处于警备状态\NTell him sector eight is now active.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.16,0:41:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，贝拉长官\NRight away, Mr. Bella.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.23,0:41:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要审讯更多的人\NAnd I want some interrogations made
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.10,0:41:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从市长开始\Nstarting with the Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.60,0:41:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听够他的笑话了\NI'm sick of his pleasantries.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.27,0:41:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\NConsider it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.34,0:41:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达瑞尔，他连苍蝇都不敢杀\NDaryl. He wouldn't hurt a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.41,0:41:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解我儿子，他决不会当游击队\NI know my son, Colonel.He's not the guerilla type.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.35,0:41:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据学校记录，市长\NAccording to the records, Mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.55,0:41:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子是优秀的学生会领袖\Nyour son is a prominent student leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.79,0:41:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，有其父必有其子\NYes. Well, he is a leader,but not in a violent or physical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.29,0:42:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，达瑞尔是个政治家的料，就像我\NNo, you see, Daryl is more of a politician, like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.97,0:42:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还是准军事组织“侦察鹰”的成员\NA member of an elite paramilitary organization, Eagle Scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.14,0:42:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是军事组织\NYes, but that's not military.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.88,0:42:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校，他要是还活着，一定又饿又怕\NNow look, Colonel, if he's alive,he's scared, he's hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.05,0:42:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定像你我一样是和平主义者\Nand he's just as anxious to avoid conflicts as you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.35,0:42:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会惹事的\NHe's not a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.98,0:42:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那谁会？\NThen who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.16,0:42:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些家族就不同了\NWell, let's just say it runs in some of the families.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.36,0:42:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里幸好有你这样识时务的俊杰\NThis community is indeed fortunate to have a shepherd like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.26,0:42:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（讽刺的笑）\N(BOTH CHUCKLING SARCASTICALLY)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.54,0:42:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想大家和平共处\NWell I, I just want to see this thing through, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.94,0:42:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有问题尽管找我，随时候命\NIf you have any more problems, call me,night or day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.81,0:42:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.88,0:42:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,审讯结束\NWe're finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.95,0:42:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时而言\Nfor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.72,0:43:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,广播播放苏联国歌\N(SOVIET NATIONAL ANTHEM PLAYING ON PA)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.83,0:43:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西班牙语\N(ORDERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.13,0:43:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西班牙语\N(ORDERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.78,0:44:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人唱《美丽的美国》\N(MAN SINGING AMERICA THE BEAUTIFUL)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.39,0:44:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多人参与\N(PEOPLE JOINING IN)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.96,0:44:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续唱歌\N(SINGING CONTINUES)
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.92,0:45:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣声\N(PEOPLE CRYING)
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.36,0:45:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,广播持续播放苏联国歌\N(SOVIET NATIONAL ANTHEM CONTINUES PLAYING ON PA)
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.38,0:45:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭，不要流泪！\NDon't cry! Hold it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.08,0:45:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要把注意力转移\NLet it turn to something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.49,0:45:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要关心的是将来\NJust let it turn to something else, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.36,0:45:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\NListen to me! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.47,0:46:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了，只要活着就别哭了\NDon't cry. Don't you ever cry again as long as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.44,0:46:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要活着就别再哭了\NAs long as you live, never do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.97,0:46:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听见没？\NYou hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.58,0:46:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会杀了我们的，我们所有人\NDANNY: They're gonna kill us! All of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.45,0:46:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那干嘛不反抗？\NSo why should we be different?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.63,0:46:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想想以后吧，迈特\NLet it turn to something else, Mattie.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.70,0:46:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想以后吧\NLet it turn, let it turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.50,0:47:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）给我汽油\N(IN RUSSIAN) Take gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.07,0:47:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小妞，你在这干嘛？\NHey, girl, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.98,0:47:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美女，你要到哪去？\NHey, beautiful, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.65,0:47:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（抗议）\N(PROTESTING)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.08,0:47:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）别闹了，把东西拿来得了\N(IN RUSSIAN) Forget the broad,just get her stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.02,0:47:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪去？\NSOLDIER: (IN RUSSIAN)Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.16,0:47:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是，等等，怎么回事？\NYou're so beautiful.Wait, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.90,0:47:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住她\NLet's get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.28,0:47:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（呜咽）\N(WHIMPERING)
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.53,0:48:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边跑\NRun. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.21,0:48:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄罗斯军官下令）\N(OFFICER ORDERING IN RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.20,0:48:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狼獾\NWolverines!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.77,0:48:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）被切断了\N(IN RUSSIAN) It's cut... It's cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.64,0:49:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前见过他们\NI've seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.81,0:50:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们曾出现在尼加拉瓜、柬埔寨、安哥拉和墨西哥\NNicaragua, El Salvador,Cambodia, Angola and Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.75,0:50:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这些是我的同胞\NBut these are my men!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.60,0:50:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄罗斯口音）小姐，你跟我说说\N(RUSSIAN ACCENT) Miss, maybe you speak at me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.30,0:50:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来，好吗？\NI'll be right back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.23,0:50:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你带女友来了？-没错\N- You bring girlfriend?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.97,0:50:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我马上回来，回见\NOkay, I be right here. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.57,0:50:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（西班牙语）什么是“狼獾”？\N(IN SPANISH) What is a '"Wolverine'"?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.84,0:50:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（西班牙语回答）一种像獾的小动物\N(RESPONDING IN SPANISH) A small animal
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.48,0:50:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但非常凶猛\Nlike a badger, but terribly ferocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.75,0:50:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是本地体育组织的名称\NIt is also the name of the local school sports collective.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.19,0:50:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是野兽\NThey're beasts, Ernesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.59,0:50:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须把他们斩尽杀绝\NYou must kill every one of them eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.16,0:50:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就像阿富汗的恐怖分子\NIt's the same as Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.93,0:50:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们永远不罢手\NThey'll never stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.36,0:51:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直站在游击队的一方\NLook, I was always on the side of the insurgents.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.44,0:51:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这种镇压经验\NI have no experience in these matters
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.17,0:51:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望得到当地人的支持\Nbut it would seem necessary to win the support of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.08,0:51:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我们的敌人在越战中所说的…\NAs our opponents used to say in Vietnam,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.01,0:51:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“赢得他们的心和思想”\N'"Win their hearts and minds.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.12,0:51:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样，他们就必败无疑\NAnd they lost, Ernesto...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.19,0:51:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，将军\NThat is true, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.59,0:51:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前线的战况陷入僵局\NThings are paralyzed at the front, Ernesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.56,0:51:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士气对我们至关重要\NMorale is crucial right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.93,0:51:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让士兵留在安全区\NKeep the men in the secured areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.93,0:51:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们就会忘掉“狼獾”\NYou'll see how they forget about these '"Wolverines.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.71,0:51:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（西班牙语）你没事吧\N(IN SPANISH) Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.01,0:51:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，你去看看\NYes, go and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.88,0:51:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚说什么，同志\NYou were saying, comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.21,0:51:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\NShut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.02,0:51:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生\NDoctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.76,0:52:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）叫医生…这怎么回事\N(IN RUSSIAN) Get a doctor...What's going on here?\N-12
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.76,0:52:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十一月\NNOVEMBER\N
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.98,0:52:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（喷气发动机的轰鸣）\N(JET ENGINES ROARING)
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.01,0:53:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是美国人\NYou American?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.85,0:53:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热血美国人\NRed-blooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.05,0:53:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德州首府是哪\NYeah, what's the capital of Texas?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.29,0:53:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯丁\NAustin.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.15,0:53:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对，同志！是休斯顿\NWrong, commie! It's Houston.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.16,0:53:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托，宝贝  我很冷\NPlease, darling. I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.93,0:53:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你电影看多了\NYou've seen too many movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.90,0:53:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你饿了？\NWell, you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.81,0:53:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃东西\NI could eat, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.61,0:53:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开什么飞机？\NWhat kind of plane you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.95,0:54:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N\NF-15\NWell, I did fly an F-15.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.65,0:54:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.49,0:54:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是鹰式飞机机师\NI'm an Eagle driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.50,0:54:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你\NHere, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.83,0:54:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从一个死了的苏军少校那拿来的\NI got this off a dead Russian Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.60,0:54:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-少校？-没错\N- Major, huh?- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.64,0:54:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至少应该当个少校吧\NI guess it ought to fit on a Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.82,0:54:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是领头的吗？体育健将\NYou the honcho, sport?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.22,0:54:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.32,0:54:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国空军中校安德鲁\NAndrew Tanner, Lieutenant Colonel,U.S. Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.82,0:54:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么被敌人击落的？\NHow did you get yourself shot down, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.69,0:54:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5:1，我击落了4架敌机\NIt was five to one. I got four.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.73,0:54:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是杰德\NI'm Jed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.60,0:54:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗，杰德\NHow are you doing, Jed?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.97,0:54:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还行\NGood as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.68,0:55:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西岸\NWest coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.02,0:55:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东岸\NEast coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.29,0:55:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是墨西哥\NDown here is Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.46,0:55:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一轮攻击以商业包机做掩护，像他们\NFirst wave of the attack came in\Ndisguised as a commercial charter flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.56,0:55:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80年代在阿富汗时干的一样\Nsame way they did in Afghanistan in '80.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.96,0:55:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是现在他们的装备更精良\NOnly they were crack airborne outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.67,0:55:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们飞越了落基山脉\NThey took these passes in the Rockies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.90,0:55:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们厄运的开始\NSo that's what hit Calumet.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.67,0:55:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NI guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.24,0:55:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还辅以核弹\NThey coordinated with selective nuke strikes,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.07,0:55:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的导弹精确度超乎我们的想象\Nand their missiles were hell of a lot\Nmore accurate than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.38,0:55:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们占据了达科他州的发射井\NThey took out silos here in the Dakotas
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.38,0:55:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-作为只要通信基地  -别的地方呢？\N- and key points of communication.- Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.78,0:55:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥马哈、华盛顿、堪萨斯城\NOh, like Omaha, Washington, Kansas City.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.55,0:55:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沦陷了？\NGone?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.65,0:55:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没错  -上帝\N- Yeah, that's right.- Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.86,0:55:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从墨西哥偷渡来的奸细\NInfiltrators came up illegal from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.53,0:55:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要是古巴人\NCubans, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.13,0:55:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已潜入了中西部\NThey managed to infiltrate
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.80,0:55:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德州的军事基地\NSAC bases in the Midwest,several down in Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.73,0:56:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里大肆破坏\NWreaked a hell of a lot of havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.67,0:56:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们打开美国大门…\NThey opened up the door down here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.60,0:56:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让古巴和尼加拉瓜军队…\Nand the whole Cuban and Nicaraguan armies
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.34,0:56:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长驱直入…\Ncome walking right through,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.51,0:56:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入大平原\Nrolled right up here through the Great Plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.61,0:56:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们到哪了\NHow far did they get?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.01,0:56:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堪萨斯州的夏安\NCheyenne across to Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.25,0:56:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以落基山脉作为基地，把他们挡在密西西比河\NWe held them at the Rockies and at the Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.99,0:56:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏联又增派了60个师\NAnyway, the Russians reinforced with 60 divisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.46,0:56:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把大部队从白令海峡派到阿拉斯加\NSent three whole army groups across the Bering Strait, into Alaska.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.86,0:56:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从加拿大进入，在中部会合\NCut the pipeline, came across Canada to link up here in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.57,0:56:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们英勇防守\NBut we stopped their butt cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.84,0:56:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在边境防线很牢固了\NLines have pretty much stabilized now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.21,0:56:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那欧洲方面呢？\NWhat about Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.48,0:56:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他们认为\NI guess they figured
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.92,0:56:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打了两次世界大战已经够了\Ntwice in one century was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.49,0:56:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还在观望\NThey're sitting this one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.96,0:57:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了英国\NAll except England.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.50,0:57:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们撑不了多久\NThey won't last very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.13,0:57:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏联想一举拿下美国，所以才来这里\NThe Russians need to take us in one piece.\NThat's why they're here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.74,0:57:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们双方都没用核弹\NThat's why they won't use nukes anymore\Nand we won't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.80,0:57:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在我们自己的国土上不会\NNot on our own soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.34,0:57:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这已是国际惯例\NThe whole damn thing's pretty conventional now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.71,0:57:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢？也许下周就开始\NWho knows?Maybe next week will be swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.08,0:57:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起因是什么？\NWhat started it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.12,0:57:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  一山不容二虎，我想\NI don't know.Two toughest kids on the block, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.89,0:57:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会干起来\NSooner or later they're gonna fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.92,0:57:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么简单？\NThat simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.06,0:57:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许有人忘记和平的真谛\NMaybe somebody forgot what it was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.13,0:57:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是我们的同盟？\NWho is on our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.67,0:57:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6亿怒吼的中国人\NSix hundred million screaming Chinamen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.77,0:57:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说中国有10亿人\NLast I heard,there were a billion screaming Chinamen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.81,0:57:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是过去\NThere were.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.38,0:57:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有家人吗\NYou got a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.95,0:58:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.49,0:58:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在敌后的德州被绑架了\NThey got caught behind the lines down in Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.53,0:58:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们还活着\NI like to think they're alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.47,0:58:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道苏军如何对待平民\Nbut I hear stories about what they're doing to civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.08,0:58:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校\NColonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.41,0:58:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-起来  -什么\N- Get up.- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.05,0:58:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发，去袭击装甲兵团\NWe're taking off, we're gonna go shoot up an armored column.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.85,0:58:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快，早起的鸟儿有虫吃\NLet's go. Early bird gets the worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.30,0:58:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早起的鸟儿有虫吃\NEarly bird gets the worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.80,0:59:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看树上的大砍刀\NWatch those claymores in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.31,0:59:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈特，火箭弹！\NMatt, RPG!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.42,0:59:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎样？我们这群毛头小子不赖吧\NNow, what do you think?Not bad for a bunch of kids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.76,0:59:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈会为你深感自豪的\NYour mom would be real proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.37,0:59:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天能吃上豆子就不错了\NAND Y: You think you're tough for eating beans every day?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.54,1:00:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天在丹佛有50万人…\NThere's half a million scarecrows in Denver
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.31,1:00:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有豆子吃就谢天谢地了\Nwould give anything for one mouthful of what you got.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.18,1:00:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经被围攻3个月\NThey've been under siege for about three months.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.38,1:00:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们吃的是老鼠和面包渣\NThey live on rats and sawdust bread and sometimes
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.15,1:00:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至人肉\Non each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.69,1:00:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚\NAt night
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.43,1:00:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,焚尸的火光照亮夜空\Nthe pyres for the dead light up the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.27,1:00:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像中世纪\NIt's medieval.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.56,1:00:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨的火焰会令你倍感煎熬\NAll that hate's gonna burn you up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.79,1:00:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我温暖\NKeeps me warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.17,1:01:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校\NColonel,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.14,1:01:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这么做是对的吗？\Nare we doing right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.36,1:02:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们交了个新朋友\NYou've made a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.23,1:02:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（咯咯的笑）\N(CHUCKLES)
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.86,1:02:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.93,1:02:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她话不多，对吧\NShe doesn't say much, does she?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.33,1:02:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.27,1:02:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定出事了\NSomething happened to her.\N-13
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.27,1:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十二月\NDECEMBER\N
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.36,1:02:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，飞机……\NAll right, plane, plane, plane, plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.13,1:02:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古巴和苏联的侦察机还有军用帐篷\NCuban bunker, Russian bunker,munitions dump, troop tents.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.57,1:02:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里、这里和这里都有碉堡\NMachine gun bunkers here,here, here, and here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.17,1:02:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里关的是政治犯\NBack here by the drive-in screen\Nare your political prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.67,1:02:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要把同胞们转移，先得切断他们的通讯\NAll right. We'll cause a diversion over here,\Ncut holes in the wire here,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.48,1:02:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打掉这些机枪\Nfire on these machine gun positions.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.01,1:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B组负责两翼的机动部队\NThe B-group comes across this area in a flanking maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.82,1:02:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你们到达碉堡处…\NWhen you reach this bunker
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.55,1:03:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低伸火力向A野战组攻击\Nyou lay down grazing fire on this duffle-A.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.79,1:03:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太简单了\NI think that's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.66,1:03:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁还有问题吗？\NAnybody got any questions so far?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.19,1:03:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“两翼”？\NWhat's a flank?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.66,1:03:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“A野战组”？\NERICA: A duffle-A?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.27,1:03:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，什么叫“低伸火力”？\NYeah. What's grazing fire?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.87,1:03:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我要喝酒  -为什么不向他们射击？\N- I need a drink.- Why don't we shoot at them?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.97,1:03:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站成一排\NMAN ON PA: Step into the line
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.49,1:03:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（西班牙语）求救！“狼獾”在偷袭我们\N(IN SPANISH) Help! Listen to me,The Wolverines are attacking!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.56,1:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跟我来\NFollow me quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.93,1:03:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\NHurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.96,1:03:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狼獾\NROBERT: Wolverines!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.08,1:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走！干掉它！快！\NMove! Take it! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.25,1:04:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-快！-快离开！\N- Come on!- Quick! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.16,1:04:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！最后机会，快！\NCome on! Here's your chance! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.29,1:04:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人难免一死，要重于泰山\NWe're all gonna die! Die standing up!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.24,1:04:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手榴弹\NGrenade!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.07,1:04:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语，诀别）\N(BIDS FAREWELL IN RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.68,1:05:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）这是毛头小子干的\NGENERAL: (IN RUSSIAN) Children did this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.22,1:05:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是游击队\NIt's rebels.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.79,1:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么游击队？是强盗\NWhat rebels? They're bandits.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.43,1:05:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次他们偷袭，革命形势就会更高涨\NEvery time they shoot,the revolution grows.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.60,1:05:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，我也曾是游击队员\NI know. I was a partisan.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.20,1:05:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你现在是什么？\NAnd now what are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.87,1:05:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我像你…\NNow I'm like you,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.97,1:05:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是秘密警察\Na policeman.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.45,1:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，上校\NAll right, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.92,1:05:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，他卧倒了\NAll right. And he's down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.76,1:05:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈特的好把戏\NGreat play by Matt Eckert.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.76,1:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.96,1:05:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-防守，伙计  -好的\N- Huddle up, folks.- Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.26,1:05:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一回很不错\NJED: That's a pretty good catch.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.27,1:06:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你掩护迈特\NROBERT: You cover Matt in this play.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.00,1:06:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.24,1:06:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地上很硬是吧\NIt's hard down on the ground, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.81,1:06:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没错  -起来吧，老头\N- Yeah.- Come on, old man. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.31,1:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\NCome down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.69,1:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子多大了\NHow old's your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.02,1:06:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子多大了\NHow old's your wife?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.42,1:06:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N\N80\NEighty.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.86,1:06:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她长的什么样\NWhat's she like?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.36,1:06:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我一样老\NOld like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.63,1:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到底什么样子\NWhat's she really like?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.93,1:06:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很活泼\NFeisty.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.60,1:06:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你\NLike you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.34,1:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在哪认识的\NWhere did you meet her?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.94,1:06:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想知道\NYou really wanna know this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.71,1:06:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.58,1:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在一个聚会的洗手间认识她的\NI met her in a closet at a party.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.15,1:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我的第一印象很不好\NCouldn't stand her at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.68,1:06:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但爱情一旦开始\NBut once it took,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.22,1:06:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(CLICKS TONGUE)
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.82,1:06:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常爱她，爱得心都疼了\NI loved her so bad, it hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.66,1:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然深爱她吗\NStill love her like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.86,1:07:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打了吗\NAre you quitters playing or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.03,1:07:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打了\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.73,1:07:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NFine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.27,1:07:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-过来！-接得好，罗伯特\N- Come on!- Good catch, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.71,1:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把孩子带来了\NThey brought their kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.48,1:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他们没有食物过冬\NThey didn't have food to feed them through the winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.25,1:07:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想把孩子给你，杰德\NThey want to give them to you, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.08,1:07:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了，梅森，我不需要更多孩子了\NThis is enough, Mr. Mason.I don't want any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.92,1:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是领袖了\NYou're a leader now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.56,1:07:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们久仰你的大名\NThey've heard of you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.29,1:07:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许在加州也是威名远扬\NMaybe all the way to California.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.83,1:07:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还打算春天派特种兵…\NAnd there are some that say\Nthey're gonna drop in some special forces
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.37,1:07:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来救你出去\Nin the spring, to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.57,1:07:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝雷帽特种兵\NGreen Berets.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.28,1:07:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离春天还远着呢\NSpring's a long time away.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.41,1:07:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从长计议吧\NIt's a lot of talk until then.\N-14
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.61,1:08:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一月\NJANUARY\N
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.34,1:08:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸\N(SONIC BOOM)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.87,1:08:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喷气发动机的轰鸣\N(JET ENGINES ROARING)
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.81,1:08:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我方战机\NIt's ours! It's ours!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.68,1:08:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\NHow can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.55,1:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我方的\NIt's ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.12,1:08:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.26,1:08:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轰掉他们\NFry 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.29,1:09:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.67,1:09:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得克服恐惧\NYou gotta cross that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.00,1:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有一点\NJust part of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.87,1:09:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们的人还在\NHope our guys are still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.94,1:09:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是战场\NSo this is a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.05,1:09:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真正的战争，孩子\NIt's a real war, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.55,1:09:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里每天都战火不断\NIt's here every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.32,1:09:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来，杰德\NCome with me, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.36,1:09:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你可以离开了\NYou can quit now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.06,1:09:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗\NCould you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.56,1:09:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别废话\NDon't give me that crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.47,1:09:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上醒来\NWake up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.97,1:09:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都会变老\NGrow old.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.04,1:10:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走！快走\NMove it! Come on! Move it!Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.09,1:10:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.22,1:10:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下…\NDown! Down! Down!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.73,1:10:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下！他看不到我们\NStay down! He can't see us!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.79,1:10:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在找我们\NDANNY: He's looking for us!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.80,1:10:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是\NSure is.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.00,1:11:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼恐惧中\N(DANNY EX CLAIMING IN FEAR)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.67,1:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了\NI can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.27,1:11:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下！\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.47,1:11:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-趴下！-闭嘴\N- Get down, get down!- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.14,1:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.56,1:11:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼尖叫\N(DANNY SCREAMING)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.79,1:11:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快跑！大家快跑\NAll right, run! Everybody get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.23,1:11:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.73,1:11:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的\NGod damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.50,1:11:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊\NChrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.73,1:11:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（尖叫）\N(SCREAMING)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.83,1:11:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心上面\NMATT: Coming up there!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.07,1:11:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（机枪射击）\N(MACHINE GUNS FIRING)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.61,1:11:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干掉他了\NI got him!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.38,1:11:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别去，杰德，那里火力太猛了\NGet out of here, Jed!There's a world of hurt coming down!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.78,1:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-滚开！-我要和你在一起，上校\N- Get out!- I'm staying with you, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.13,1:12:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快带他走\NJED: Take him out with the RPG, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.43,1:12:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一枚火箭弹\NROBERT: Give me another rocket!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.61,1:12:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,土豚\NAardvark!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.86,1:12:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的厉害\NEat me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.54,1:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（呻吟）\N(GROANING)
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.54,1:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要…\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.08,1:13:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，伙计，来干掉他们\NCome on, buddies, come and get them!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.25,1:13:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一击即中\NShoot straight for once,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.62,1:13:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这帮小子\Nyou army pukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.43,1:13:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.83,1:13:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没用的，他死了\NIt's useless. He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.70,1:13:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.90,1:13:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\NGo! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.24,1:13:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坦克炮发射\N(TANK TURRET WHIRRING)
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.38,1:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会爱上其他人了\NI'll never love anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.91,1:14:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会爱上其他人了\NI'll never love anybody again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.09,1:14:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不爱别人，你就不会在这里了\NIf you didn't love anybody,you'd never even be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.13,1:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在哪里安葬他\NWhere are we gonna bury him?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.73,1:14:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么好安葬的\NWhat's left to bury?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.97,1:14:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊…\NOh, God. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.61,1:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是好朋友\NThese were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.14,1:14:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝吧他们带走\NTake them away from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.31,1:14:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带到天堂安息之所\NSomeplace safe
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.05,1:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里永无战争\Nwhere this war's never happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.79,1:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远怀念他们\NAnd as we remember,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.79,1:14:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主啊，让他们忘却所有痛苦\NPlease let them forget, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.60,1:14:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们就能安息\Nso they can be little again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.70,1:14:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.31,1:15:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰德\NMATT: (WHISPERING) Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.68,1:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰德\N(HISSING) Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.95,1:15:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在嘟囔什么\NWhat are you whispering for?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.28,1:15:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很宁静\NFeels quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.79,1:15:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该睡一会\NYou should get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.72,1:15:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很晚了\NIt's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.06,1:15:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事\NI'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.03,1:15:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气氛很奇怪，是吧\NIt's kind of strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.03,1:15:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大山对我们毫不在意\NHow the mountains pay us no attention at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.84,1:15:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是喜是悲\NYou laugh or you cry,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.87,1:15:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风依旧在吹\Nthe wind just keeps on blowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.98,1:15:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人谁无死\NIt was bound to happen sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.55,1:15:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太感情用事了，对吧\NYou're getting pretty lean on feelings,aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.59,1:15:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能这样\NCan't afford them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.69,1:15:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是因为我\NEven if that had been me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.90,1:15:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说我们小队\NI was talking to the group, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.46,1:16:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们士气低落，大家都想放弃了\NDoesn't look good.They're all talking about quitting.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.83,1:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都不想再打仗了\NSeems like they lost the stomach for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.34,1:16:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了罗伯特\NExcept for Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.91,1:16:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\NAnd you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.64,1:16:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你兄弟\NI'm your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.44,1:16:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定支持你\NJust make it count.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.98,1:16:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄语\N(SPEAKING RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.41,1:17:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）起立！\N(IN RUSSIAN) Attention!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.29,1:17:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐下，同志们\N(IN RUSSIAN) Be seated, comrades.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.43,1:17:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最蔑视的就是这种伪善\NWhat I despise most about warfare\Nis the hypocrisy it often breeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.57,1:17:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说我方考虑和…\NI've heard euphemisms\Nthat we are containing the enemy
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.44,1:17:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方和谈的呼声日益高涨\Nthat our sector of pacification is growing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.81,1:17:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是缓兵之计的谎言\NThese are the tactics of the lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.68,1:17:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谎言会带来死亡和失败\NLies have the stench of death and defeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.89,1:18:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有斩草除根才能真正获胜\NYou can only win a war by exterminating the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.63,1:18:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们的敌人是谁吗\NDo you know who we are fighting?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.73,1:18:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是狼獾\NWe are fighting wolverines,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.07,1:18:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穷凶极恶的游击队\Nsmall ferocious animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.94,1:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要歼灭他们需要高明的猎手\NFor them you need a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.18,1:18:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本人就是\NAnd you know, I am a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.85,1:18:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后\NFrom this moment on,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.19,1:18:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们再不会进行报复平民的行动\Nthere will be no further reprisals against civilians.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.96,1:18:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太愚蠢了\NThat was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.60,1:18:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不起作用\NImpotence.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.27,1:18:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同志们\NComrades,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.17,1:18:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是狐狸偷了你的鸡\Nif a fox stole your chickens,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.38,1:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会因为猪看见了，就杀猪吗？当然不\Nwould you slaughter your pig because he saw the fox? No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.62,1:19:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会猎杀狐狸\NYou would hunt the fox,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.29,1:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到它的老巢然后歼灭它\Nfind where it lives and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.50,1:19:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们该咋办呢\NAnd how do we do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.67,1:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成狐狸\NBecome a fox.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.87,1:19:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(WARBLING RHYTHMICALLY)
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.24,1:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SENSOR WARBLING)
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.58,1:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MEN SCREAMING)
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.75,1:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MEN MOANING)
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.16,1:21:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(GUN FIRES)
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.74,1:21:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼，保险打开了\NDanny, bolt's open.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.31,1:21:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡住了\NIt's jammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.75,1:21:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼\NDanny. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.09,1:21:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(INQUIRING IN GERMAN)
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.39,1:22:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他是装的呢？你怎么知道\NSo what if he does? You don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.16,1:22:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们最好离开\NWe better get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.16,1:22:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(INQUIRING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.56,1:22:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死他\NShoot him!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.76,1:22:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\NWhat is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.96,1:22:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.93,1:22:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在追杀我们？\NWho's coming after us?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.50,1:22:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在哪？\NWhere are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.51,1:22:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砸破他脑袋\NRub a butt on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.17,1:22:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(EX CLAIMS)
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.84,1:22:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！太阳你木琴的！\N(IN ENGLISH) Suck at you!God damn for your mother!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.71,1:22:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有刀，就会把你脑袋砍掉\NI hear a chopper and I'm gonna blow your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.58,1:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚你玛勒隔壁的美国恶棍\NGo die, Yankee! Die!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.42,1:22:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的杂种\NGod damn, you son of...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.82,1:22:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是高尔斯基，你们这些狗娘养的混球\NGorsky, Stepan Yevgenyvitch. Suck it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.82,1:22:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁塔麻管你叫什么\NNo one gives a damn who you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.89,1:22:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们会伤到他  -好极了\N- They're gonna hurt him!- Good!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.73,1:22:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看\NHey, hey, hey, hey! Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.36,1:22:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有指南针\NThis thing's got an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.36,1:22:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指着…\NIt's pointing. It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.10,1:22:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.73,1:22:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(=@__@=)哪里？\NWhere? Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.84,1:22:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里\NRight here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.45,1:22:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达瑞尔\NDaryl.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.72,1:23:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(WARBLING FASTER)
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.42,1:23:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.52,1:23:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？\NWhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.29,1:23:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？\NWhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.00,1:23:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的，追踪器在哪？\NGod damn it, where's the bug?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.13,1:23:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他们逼我吞了  -达瑞尔，你为什么背叛我们？\N- They made me swallow it.- Daryl, what have you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.47,1:23:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我进城去…\NI went into town.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.84,1:23:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被抓住了\NAnd got caught.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.64,1:23:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被抓住了！\NAnd went and got caught!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.21,1:23:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.68,1:23:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说我们不该进城\NBecause you said we couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.15,1:23:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的位置是你告诉敌人的？\NROBERT: You told them where we were, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.22,1:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你告的密！\NYou told them!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.19,1:23:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我爸举报我的\NMy father turned me in.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.29,1:23:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝，他们折磨我的手段，你们根本想象不到\NOh, God,they did things you can't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.53,1:23:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(EX CLAIMING)
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.43,1:23:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这婊子养的！\NYou son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.20,1:23:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要眼罩吗\NYou want blindfolds?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.17,1:23:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是违反日内瓦条约的\NThis violate the Geneva Convention.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.87,1:23:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没听说过日内瓦条约\NI never heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.94,1:23:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！让你看看苏联汉子怎样直面死亡！\NDogface! I show you how Soviet dies!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.84,1:24:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也直面死亡过，伙计\NI've seen it before, pal.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.85,1:24:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的！不是真的！\NThis isn't happening! This isn't happening!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.68,1:24:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰德，放了他！ -闭嘴，丹尼\N- Jed, let him go!- Shut up, Danny!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.35,1:24:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他是我们自己人！ -闭嘴！\N- He was one of us!- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.75,1:24:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他向敌军告发我们的位置\NHe told them where we were!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.82,1:24:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的确出卖了我们\NHe did.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.72,1:24:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-拿起来复枪  -不要\N- Now, get your rifles.- No!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.09,1:24:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.23,1:24:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说不！我们不能这样！\NI said no! We're not doing it!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.63,1:24:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小子，说我们是朋友吧\NBoy, say that you are friend
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.13,1:24:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用当孤魂野鬼\Nso I will not die alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.80,1:24:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么区别？杰德\NWhat's the difference, Jed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.17,1:24:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我来处决他们  -闭嘴！罗伯特\N- I'll do it.- Shut up, Robert!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.37,1:24:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，我们跟他们有什么区别？\NTell me, what's the difference between us and them?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.75,1:24:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是美国人\NBecause we live here!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.95,1:24:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SCREAMING)
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.06,1:24:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪，别…\NDon't shoot. Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.13,1:24:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别杀我，杰德\NDon't shoot me, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.49,1:24:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别杀我，杰德\NDon't shoot me, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.86,1:24:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(STIFLING SCREAM)
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.87,1:24:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.75,1:27:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(KEENING)
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.34,1:27:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(IMITATES BIRD CALL)
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.34,1:28:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还剩下几个人\NHow many of those you got left?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.24,1:28:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四个\NFour.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.98,1:28:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预备——\NReady.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.39,1:28:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，等等，别这样，停下\NNo, wait. Don't. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.70,1:28:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎样？\NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.27,1:28:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你饿了吗？\NYou hungry?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.48,1:28:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饿了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.85,1:29:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(IMITATES BIRD CALL)
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.65,1:29:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，托妮\NJED: (WHISPERING) Go, Toni.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.42,1:29:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(INAUDIBLE)
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.56,1:29:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(IMITATES BIRD CALL)
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.53,1:30:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快拿，回到岩石那儿再吃\NJED: Let's get it fast and get back to the rock.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.26,1:30:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.59,1:30:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没吃到这些了\NIt's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.45,1:31:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(HELICOPTER WHIRRING DISTANTLY)
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.42,1:31:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小声点…\NQuiet, quiet, quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.99,1:31:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(HELICOPTER APPROACHING)
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.07,1:31:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MACHINE GUNS FIRING)
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.64,1:31:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊\NTONI: Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.45,1:31:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊\NROBERT: Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.42,1:31:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卧倒！\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.82,1:31:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-托妮！-趴下\NERICA: Toni!JED: Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.29,1:31:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卧倒\NStay down!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.79,1:32:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-快离开这！ -快\N- Let's get out of here!- Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.50,1:32:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.10,1:32:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走…\NCome on. Get on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.14,1:32:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\NYeah. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.18,1:32:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\NJED: Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.18,1:32:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\NGo on! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.30,1:33:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托妮\NToni!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.20,1:33:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托妮\NToni!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.29,1:34:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狼獾\NWolverines!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.41,1:35:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快死了，杰德\NI'm killed, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.12,1:35:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们活捉我\NDon't let them get me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.92,1:35:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定会逼我招供\NBecause they'll make me talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.13,1:36:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的枪呢？\NWhere's your gun?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.57,1:36:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想死在你手上\NI want you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.38,1:36:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(COCKS GUN)
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.66,1:36:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下不了手\NI can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.03,1:36:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托妮，我狠不了心\N(STIFLING SOB) I can't, Toni. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.96,1:36:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.10,1:36:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.87,1:36:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的手榴弹给我\NGive me your grenade.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.91,1:36:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想冷冷清清地死\NI don't wanna be too cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.16,1:36:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我拔掉保险栓\NPull the pin for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.84,1:37:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想待在这…\NI'm just gonna stay here
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.74,1:37:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这倾听风的声音，可以吗？\Nand listen to the wind a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.35,1:37:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.00,1:38:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校同志\N(IN RUSSIAN) Comrade Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.53,1:38:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我预计约有12具敌尸\NI would estimate enemy body count at 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.14,1:38:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12具\NTwelve...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.51,1:39:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不同意吗？\NWouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.98,1:39:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12具\NTwelve.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.25,1:39:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12具\NTwelve.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.85,1:39:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只看见1具\NI saw only one.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.19,1:39:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们炸掉了同伴尸体\NBut they carry off their dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.40,1:39:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了，不可以吗？\NOf course, why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.77,1:39:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为何如此残酷？\NWhy do you think they are so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.28,1:39:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N\N(EXPLOSION)\N-15
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.58,1:40:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡同胞名单
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.58,1:40:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，听我说\NAll right, now, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.72,1:40:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩留在这，直到敌军撤回镇上\NYou two are gonna wait up here\Nuntil the troops pull back into town.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.55,1:40:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们会知道他们何时撤回\NYou'll know when that happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.12,1:40:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一走，你们就退守平原\NWhen they do, head out for the plains.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.59,1:40:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.29,1:40:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留守这里\NI gotta stick around.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.26,1:40:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引起敌人注意，这样你们才能顺利逃脱\NStir things up, so you can make it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.60,1:40:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们要和你共进退，迈特  -不行\N- We're going with you, Mattie.- No.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.80,1:40:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们要和你共进退   -听我说\N- We're going with you.- Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.60,1:40:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们小队就剩我们几个了\NWe are all that's left.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.40,1:40:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留得青山在  你们一定要逃出去\NSomeone's gotta live.Somebody's gotta make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.54,1:40:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和杰德已经没用了\NMe and Jed, we're all used up.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.15,1:40:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.02,1:40:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.83,1:40:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远忘不了你们\NI'm never gonna forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.53,1:40:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还活着\NAs long as I live.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.27,1:41:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远忘不了\NNever forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.74,1:41:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,铭记终生\NDon't.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.21,1:41:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈特\NMatt.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.51,1:41:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不知鹿死谁手呢\NYou're never gonna know who won.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.12,1:41:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会赢的\NWe will.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.42,1:41:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定能逃出去，杰德\NYou know, we could make it, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.49,1:41:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前经历的比这严峻得多\NWe've been a lot tougher than this before.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.83,1:41:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们转移到山上吧\NWe cause a diversion, get out of here,\Nhead back to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.90,1:41:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你，迈特\NI love you, Mattie.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.67,1:41:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.74,1:41:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你，杰德\NI love you, too, Jed.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.46,1:42:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可谓难兄难弟\NIt's hard being brothers, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.33,1:42:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.52,1:42:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.82,1:42:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不记得温暖的感觉了\N(IN SPANISH) I can't remember what it was to be warm
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.40,1:42:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得只有很小的时候，才感受过阳光的温暖\NIt seems a thousand years since I was a small boy in the sun
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.24,1:42:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎会来到这荒无人烟的崇山峻岭\NHow did I come to this high,desolate place
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.61,1:42:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有孤寂\Nwhere there is nothing but loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.11,1:42:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了很多很多\NSo much is lost
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.32,1:43:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想凝视你的双眼，忘记一切烦忧\NI want to look in your eyes and forget
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.29,1:43:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远离尘嚣\NIt all seems so far away
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.29,1:43:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温暖的房子，我不再形单影只\NA warm house where my shadow never falls,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.83,1:43:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的双手，穿过你乌黑的长发\Nyour long, black hair in my hands
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.17,1:43:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也没有动荡\NThere is no more revolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.54,1:43:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你是我心灵的港湾\Nonly you to come back to
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.61,1:43:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会递上辞呈\NI will post my resignation
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.95,1:43:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(EXPLOSION)
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.22,1:43:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(EXPLOSION)
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.55,1:43:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MEN SHOUTING)
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.52,1:43:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MACHINE GUNS FIRING)
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.07,1:43:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SCREAMING)
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.02,1:44:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MACHINE GUN FIRING)
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.00,1:44:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SPEAKING RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.26,1:44:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！快走！…\NCome on! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.93,1:44:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SPEAKING SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.04,1:45:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(SHOUTING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.48,1:45:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(EXPLOSION)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.22,1:45:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(EXPLOSION)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.02,1:45:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MACHINE GUNS FIRING)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.92,1:45:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(CHATTERING IN RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.80,1:45:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在偷袭岗哨\N(IN RUSSIAN) They're attacking the station!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.94,1:45:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快到岗哨那里\N(IN RUSSIAN) Everybody to the station!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.41,1:45:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(WHISTLE BLOWING)
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.51,1:45:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MAN CHATTERING INDISTINCTLY)
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.60,1:46:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（俄语）快！快！\N(IN RUSSIAN) Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.52,1:47:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MEN CHATTERING IN RUSSIAN)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.67,1:47:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你输了\NYou lose.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.78,1:47:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(COUGHS)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.42,1:48:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N(MUTTERING GOODBYE IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.47,1:48:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以安息了\NYou can rest now.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.84,1:48:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，迈特\NJust hang on, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.32,1:48:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，迈特\NOh, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.55,1:48:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，迈特，没事的\NIt's okay, Matt. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.85,1:48:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住，迈特，爸爸很快就来了\NJust hang on, Matt.Daddy will be here soon, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.02,1:48:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住，迈特\NHang on, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.60,1:48:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撑住，迈特，爸爸很快就要来了\NCome on, Matt. Daddy will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.94,1:48:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了，迈特\NIt's okay. Come on, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.92,1:49:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直抱着你的，迈特\NI'll hold you as long as I can, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.22,1:49:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直抱着你\NI'll hold you as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.99,1:49:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以靠着我\NYou can lean on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.06,1:49:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很累\NI'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.57,1:49:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太累了\NSo tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.18,1:50:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在自由了\NWe're free now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.15,1:50:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由了\NFree.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.49,1:50:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也没见过这兄弟俩\NERICA: I never saw the brothers again
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.86,1:50:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争\NIn time, this war,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.50,1:50:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久就结束了\Nlike every other war, ended
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.13,1:50:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我永远无法忘怀\NBut I never forgot
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.90,1:50:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经常旧地重游\NAnd I come to this place often
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.44,1:50:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(游击队碑)\N虽然只有我一个人\NThough no one else does
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.21,1:50:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第三次世界大战初期\NIn the early days of World War III,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.85,1:50:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游击队成员大多是少年\Nguerillas, mostly children,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.15,1:50:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将失去的同伴名字刻在这块岩石之上\Nplaced the names of their lost upon this rock
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.49,1:50:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在此孤军奋战\NThey fought here alone
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.12,1:50:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献出自己宝贵的生命\Nand gave up their lives
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.69,1:50:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以保卫祖国的安全与完整\Nso that this nation shall not perish from the earth
